{"tid":2139012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"謝偉俊: 不獲延任者不應只4人 原應被DQ民主派亦要被OUT","createTime":"2020-08-04T04:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T05:08:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"713fa49c8c03b29f037a3a4add18546f1072706c","tid":2139012,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/RLL54XIAYL7CVJNNI6JLU55XXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FRLL54XIAYL7CVJNNI6JLU55XXE%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Ydwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=08b45b90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FRLL54XIAYL7CVJNNI6JLU55XXE%2F&h=b56b1454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/RLL54XIAYL7CVJNNI6JLU55XXE/</a><br />\n<br />\n港澳辦副主任張曉明連日在中聯辦會晤各界就立法會「真空期」收集意見，全國政協常委唐英年今早亦進入了中聯辦大樓。謝偉俊亦是座上客，他今早於電台節目未透露會面內容，只稱個人認為並非全部民主派議員都可以「翻閹」延任，直指除了4名參選時遭DQ的民主派議員不能續延任外，其他本應被DQ但未被正式DQ的民主派議員，選舉主任亦應繼續一併DQ，令他們不能在未來一年續任議員，直言：「喺（立法會任期）四年加一年嘅過程中，係有個選擇性嘅過程」。"},{"pid":"1788d946b0673b4effeec3a10faecf80c6ecde98","tid":2139012,"uid":127575,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:16:47.000Z","msg":"呢條友睇得出應該冇外國資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心甘情願永世做大灣區人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d8d8006c1b48e49e5574580232e9c988a5fb74","tid":2139012,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1788d946b0673b4effeec3a10faecf80c6ecde98","tid":2139012,"uid":127575,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:16:47.000Z","msg":"呢條友睇得出應該冇外國資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心甘情願永世做大灣區人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=